name: Cancer Awareness Charity Mini Bag Charm.
description:
We are supported by Yorkshire Cancer Research (reg charity no. 516898).
Measures approximately 10cm in length. 
Profits go directly to Yorkshire Cancer Research. 
Let's try beat cancer together for all those still fighting and those that can't be with us anymore but remain in our hearts.
